<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="82" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="12.[136,1452,947,1046]" pageId="12" pageNumber="82">
Leaves shorter or longer than scape, margins mostly ciliate. 
<emphasis box="[829,979,947,973]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="82">Inflorescence</emphasis>
conical or oblong-ovoid; pedicels longer than flowers in fruiting raceme, horizontal, ascending or recurved. 
<emphasis box="[914,1012,983,1009]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="82">Perianth</emphasis>
tubular-campanulate, white, purple to green, with green veining on lobes. 
<emphasis box="[537,624,1019,1045]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="82">Anthers</emphasis>
violet. 
<emphasis box="[709,801,1019,1045]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="82">Capsule</emphasis>
valves obovate-elliptic with cuneate base.
</paragraph>
